Package Model

Class OrderDetail

java.lang.Object
Model.OrderDetail
public class OrderDetail
extends java.lang.Object
A mirror of the "client" table from the "schooldb" database. It is the internal representation of the table. This class and its corresponding table were created to solve the ONE-TO-MANY relationship between an order and its associated products. Unlike the other models, the OrderDetail does not have a unique identification key and all fields may repeat their values.
